	when libFoundation is used.  In the standard case, we no longer
	add the -Ixxx/Headers/gnustep/ flags.
	* library-combo.make (GNUSTEP_FND_DIR): Do not define.
	* rules.make (ALL_OBJCFLAGS): Removed GNUSTEP_HEADERS_FND_FLAG.
